{"tid":2355474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《環球時報》記者機場遇襲案 三被告暴動罪成 測量師脫罪","createTime":"2021-01-06T06:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T19:36:55.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a732380a7db3f674fa4860c7fb03e294c1c7576f","tid":2355474,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"自稱《環球時報》記者的中國人付國豪，前年8月在機場遭示威者綑綁及圍堵，歷時接近兩小時。事後「佔旺女村長」畢慧芬及兼職侍應賴雲龍等四人被控暴動、傷人與非法禁錮等八罪，案件今在區域法院裁決。<br />\n<br />\n法官李慶年今裁定其中三人暴動等三罪成立，而被控非法禁錮及非法集結罪的測量師則兩罪均不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/392s8MB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F392s8MB&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=1e8d86b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/392s8MB</a>"},{"pid":"71d55380a10d6b8f9d7620c807d49570c838d7bf","tid":2355474,"uid":214502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:37:46.000Z","msg":"唔係政見唔同互相打鬥?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5bc18a2362f9404a18d33bbb999777862bb700a","tid":2355474,"uid":261873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"邊忽記者<br />\n都無記者證、工作證"},{"pid":"c07dacfb82ec3993c2adf93e6bdbe61b3ad4d1e5","tid":2355474,"uid":57205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"明明係假記者"},{"pid":"f3dc12157c655c018d32589e360b66110b559226","tid":2355474,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:36:55.000Z","msg":"DLLM，白衣人一個都未告<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}